title: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: When attempting to set the color to orange, it is not applied correctly. This is a regression bug as the issue did not occur in previous versions.
OB: When setting the color to orange in the report item, the color is not applied correctly.
EB: The expected behavior is that when setting the color to orange, the color should be displayed correctly.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a report item into the report.
2. Set the color or background color of the report item to orange.
